01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627976681394176745863.png/2QKg2kn9bjZJ1N2fX4FlmluqOhVYlaf49PonWPT6J1g\" alt=\"魏登霍弗詢問退休老兵班巴斯現在為什麼仍在工作（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>魏登霍弗詢問退休老兵班巴斯現在為什麼仍在工作（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627979277799424591307.png/Ul1PF29Cve690WiplViQcjxAKg6ZwlXDiALAgYgCwIE\" alt=\"退休老兵班巴斯說明仍在工作的原因（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>退休老兵班巴斯說明仍在工作的原因（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627981559631872851472.png/m-MpwXamnglhC-zptXDFubu-bSNaEIcuE3Vj7xN1Y-8\" alt=\"退休老兵班巴斯說明仍在工作的原因（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>退休老兵班巴斯說明仍在工作的原因（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627971689910272348109.png/6W2cpfJz1vREgkFPWffmHpHl2xQY5kt_W7PQS1uz0Es\" alt=\"退休老兵班巴斯說明仍在工作的原因（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>退休老兵班巴斯說明仍在工作的原因（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627974168875008158940.png/7z3ULrMTDnuHEAQELvRAhvapYvrcyA5uaxPKL2sTyi8\" alt=\"魏登霍弗詢問退休老兵班巴斯：“那你的妻子呢”（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>魏登霍弗詢問退休老兵班巴斯：“那你的妻子呢”（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627976383598592021864.png/Nxk_4YPcBU-2t3erU3cFcC3Ejn1WiosxtjmXibY5l4k\" alt=\"退休老兵班巴斯說他妻子七年前就去世了（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>退休老兵班巴斯說他妻子七年前就去世了（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627978527019008294613.png/15-Cm9AI8bYlqFN3m_2xePAUz8pvDFEmOk3a8jpN2vI\" alt=\"退休老兵班巴斯說他妻子七年前就去世了（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>退休老兵班巴斯說他妻子七年前就去世了（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627980620107776178230.png/lvEXnNMyFWj56-nivSA1vQnL27FZHAt1yVwkYclcJGE\" alt=\"班巴斯說他自己還是退伍軍人（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>班巴斯說他自己還是退伍軍人（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627974038851584954170.png/fJqHXOkqAjvl7PcPSg1EPKSzhJhH6kT-uBMeArgTHgI\" alt=\"退休老兵班巴斯現在一周仍要工作五天（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>退休老兵班巴斯現在一周仍要工作五天（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627976727531520946083.png/C-HOcjDkgwd3XU0t1h5ZJfRLTmJINDUe-VEWvflRFr0\" alt=\"退休老兵班巴斯現在一天仍要工作八小時（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>退休老兵班巴斯現在一天仍要工作八小時（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627978896117760017823.png/pza26URtEOizfyY-yrYqMMqVomd8UU1PSInKQkiJykI\" alt=\"「我很幸運，上帝給了我健康的身體，讓我能夠每天站著工作8個多小時」，說到這裡他忍不住心酸落淚。（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>「我很幸運，上帝給了我健康的身體，讓我能夠每天站著工作8個多小時」，說到這裡他忍不住心酸落淚。（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627981282807808685743.png/ythvJlDJaihgAA5m_TrxpK8GgomY_-0MLXdvUS13b1E\" alt=\"魏登霍弗給了班巴斯400美元小費（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>魏登霍弗給了班巴斯400美元小費（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251205/1073627951276232704708316.png/KIW_AZlSZrcl1wd56CZI8yfKVA_0RjpcKDcsAig3LAI\" alt=\"班巴斯因為小費感動到哭泣（X@Collin Rugg）\"><figcaption>班巴斯因為小費感動到哭泣（X@Collin Rugg）</figcaption></figure><p>延伸閲讀：</p><p>太惡劣！6月大女嬰遭遺棄時代廣場　警方循線追查中</p><p>【本文獲「中天新聞網」授權轉載。】</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-24T03:41:59.236500+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":1999,"images":31,"source":"HK01 國際","fallback":"none"}}